  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052080/extras/90d21f27f6d3c4b8847728d9630a60bf.webp?t=1711474420\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052080/extras/54c86687c1ff716c4c5650eb772dc397.webp?t=1711474420\" width=32 height=48 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052080/extras/835b8b6e490f55fb9d517f2cf4c136f2.webp?t=1711474420\" width=16 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A cakenapping!</strong></h2><br>As the bride and groom's wedding ceremony inside an ancient castle comes to a close and they prepare to have their delicious chocolate wedding cake, a legion of fruit monsters comes out of hiding and takes off with their cake!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rescue your wedding cake!</strong></h2><br>Become the bride with her powerful shotgun, or the groom with his fast-firing sidearm, and obliterate every single fruit monster that gets in the way of your quest to rescue your cake!<br><br>You're going to have your cake and EAT IT too!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> High octane twin-stick shooting action!<br></li><li> Simple but challenging gameplay!<br></li><li> Pixel art fruit obliteration!<br></li><li> Unique Power Card perk system: level up and choose cards to flip over to gain powers.  Match two cards of the same type for extra bonuses!<br></li><li> Bride and groom local co-op!<br></li><li> A rockin' soundtrack!  <br></li><li> Full controller support<br></li><li> Plays on Steam Deck!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052080/extras/90d21f27f6d3c4b8847728d9630a60bf.webp?t=1711474420\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052080/extras/54c86687c1ff716c4c5650eb772dc397.webp?t=1711474420\" width=32 height=48 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052080/extras/835b8b6e490f55fb9d517f2cf4c136f2.webp?t=1711474420\" width=16 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A cakenapping!</strong></h2><br>As the bride and groom's wedding ceremony inside an ancient castle comes to a close and they prepare to have their delicious chocolate wedding cake, a legion of fruit monsters comes out of hiding and takes off with their cake!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rescue your wedding cake!</strong></h2><br>Become the bride with her powerful shotgun, or the groom with his fast-firing sidearm, and obliterate every single fruit monster that gets in the way of your quest to rescue your cake!<br><br>You're going to have your cake and EAT IT too!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> High octane twin-stick shooting action!<br></li><li> Simple but challenging gameplay!<br></li><li> Pixel art fruit obliteration!<br></li><li> Unique Power Card perk system: level up and choose cards to flip over to gain powers.  Match two cards of the same type for extra bonuses!<br></li><li> Bride and groom local co-op!<br></li><li> A rockin' soundtrack!  <br></li><li> Full controller support<br></li><li> Plays on Steam Deck!</li></ul>",
